  "page": "Krazaaj Zasqa",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:WorldofIceandFire.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Krazaaj Zasqa is located in The Known World\"><img alt=\"Krazaaj Zasqa is located in The Known World\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/10/WorldofIceandFire.png/300px-WorldofIceandFire.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/10/WorldofIceandFire.png/450px-WorldofIceandFire.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/10/WorldofIceandFire.png/600px-WorldofIceandFire.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 43.3%; left: 70.3%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Krazaaj Zasqa\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Krazaaj Zasqa</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a> and the location of the Krazaaj Zasqa\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Krazaaj Zasqa</b>, meaning \"White Mountains\" in the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_language\" title=\"Dothraki language\">Dothraki language</a>, is what the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> call the northern <a href=\"/index.php/Bone_Mountains\" title=\"Bone Mountains\">Bone Mountains</a> in central <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_beyond_the_free_cities:_east_of_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_beyond_the_free_cities:_east_of_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_bones_and_beyond.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_bones_and_beyond.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_krazaaj_zasqa.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_krazaaj_zasqa.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> The snow-capped<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_bones_and_beyond.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_bones_and_beyond.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> range stretches longitudinally from the <a href=\"/index.php/Shivering_Sea\" title=\"Shivering Sea\">Shivering Sea</a> and transitions southward into the rest of the Bones at the <a href=\"/index.php/Steel_Road\" title=\"Steel Road\">Steel Road</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf_the_dothraki_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf_the_dothraki_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The northern section of the Krazaaj Zasqa contains the <a href=\"/index.php/Realm_of_Jhogwin\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Realm of Jhogwin\">Realm of Jhogwin</a>. West of the mountains are the forested <a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_the_Ifequevron\" title=\"Kingdom of the Ifequevron\">Kingdom of the Ifequevron</a> and the ruined city of <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Aresak\" title=\"Vaes Aresak\">Vaes Aresak</a>, while north across the Shivering Sea is found the island of <a href=\"/index.php/Far_Ib\" title=\"Far Ib\">Far Ib</a>. East of the Krazaaj Zasqa are the <a href=\"/index.php/Howling_Hills\" title=\"Howling Hills\">Howling Hills</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Leviathan_Sound\" title=\"Leviathan Sound\">Leviathan Sound</a>, while the city of <a href=\"/index.php/Kayakayanaya\" title=\"Kayakayanaya\">Kayakayanaya</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Sand_Sea\" title=\"Great Sand Sea\">Great Sand Sea</a> are situated to the southeast along the Steel Road.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf_the_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf_the_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Krazaaj_Zasqa&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_beyond_the_free_cities:_east_of_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_beyond_the_free_cities:_east_of_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: East of Ib.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_bones_and_beyond.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_bones_and_beyond.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_bones_and_beyond.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Bones and Beyond.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiaf_krazaaj_zasqa.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiaf_krazaaj_zasqa.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  Krazaaj Zasqa.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiaf_the_dothraki_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiaf_the_dothraki_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  The Dothraki Sea.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiaf_the_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiaf_the_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  The Known World.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403095811\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.032 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.035 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 981/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12442/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4769/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2217/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3074/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   24.915      1 -total\n 45.90%   11.436      1 Template:Location_map\n 42.91%   10.692      1 Template:Location_map+\n 41.36%   10.304      6 Template:Ref\n 28.84